DESCRIPTION:Event Description: March 6 - March 29 As the first intrepid 
 bulbs and blossoms awaken in our local landscape\, Bainbridge Arts and C
 rafts will fast forward spring with our March exhibition\, “Floribunda.”
  Eleven local artists share their unique interpretations of floral abund
 ance\, some naturalistic and some abstract\, transforming the gallery in
 to a garden of imagination. Featuring artists: Lynn Fry Agnew\, Katy Gil
 more\, Sarah Gordon\, Carol Gouthro\, Chris Holt\, Molly Hueffed\, Sande
 e Johnson\, Lisa Snow Lady\, Danis Morgan\, Kim Obbink\, Annie Starling 
 Sparks. Opening reception at First Friday\, March 6\, 6–8pm.<br>Event Ty
 pes: Arts\,Community\,Education\,Museum/Gallery\,Special Events\,Tourism
 <br>Audience: All<br>Sponsoring Organization: Bainbridge Arts & Crafts<b
 r>Contact: Ari Emerson<br>Contact Phone: 206.842.3132<br>Contact Email: 
 gallery@bacart.org<br>Site Contact Details: https://www.bacart.org<br>Pr
 e-Register: No<br>Cost: Free<br>Link: https://www.bacart.org/exhibitions
 <br>
