 l<br>Pre-Register: Yes<br>Cost: Free<br>Link: https://www.langstonseattl
 e.org/programs/karate-with-tyron/<br><br>Tyron Asphy\, founder of&#160\;
 Japan-American Butokukan Karate Association\, has returned to the Langst
 on Hughes Performing Arts Institute\, where he taught community karate c
 lasses over 40 years ago.<br><br>Tyron works with five instructors to of
 fer martial arts classes to students ages 5 to 75 years old. His commitm
 ent to bringing access to discipline\, flexibility\, and self-defense to
  the Black youth and other residents in the Central District area is inv
 aluable to the overall health and well-being of our community.
