 he meeting.	</li><li>Alternatively\, sign up to speak on the public comm
 ent sign-up sheet located inside the meeting room at least 15 minutes pr
 ior to the&#160\;meeting.</li></ol>Each speaker may be allotted up to tw
 o minutes to speak.<br><br>If you are unable to attend the meeting in-pe
