 nter.com/explore/waterfront-park/central-waterfront-oversight-committee<
 br><br>The Central Waterfront Oversight Committee was established in 201
 9 by City Council Ordinance 125761. The committee&#8217\;s role is to ad
 vise and provide feedback to the City and Friends of Waterfront Park on 
