DESCRIPTION:Event Types: Arts\,Grants\,Training-Classes/Workshops<br>Nei
 ghborhoods: Citywide\,Online Event<br>Contact: Zach Frimmel<br>Contact P
 hone: (206) 963-9226<br>Contact Email: Zach.Frimmel@seattle.gov<br>Audie
 nce: All<br>Pre-Register: Yes<br>Cost: Free<br>Link: https://teams.micro
 soft.com/l/meetup-join/19%3ameeting_NjM2ZGJlOWUtNzRlYy00NDllLWI4MWYtOWNl
